attachmentList.name: Standart Stock
attachmentList.description: Improves weapon switch speed and aim sway.
attachmentList.commoneffect: Improves weapon switch speed and aim sway.
attachmentList.rareeffect: Quicker handling and moderate aim drift reduction. (Raising/lowering weapon is 25% faster)
attachmentList.epiceffect: Fast handling and large aim drift reduction. (Raising/lowering weapon is 35% faster)
attachmentList.legendaryeffect: No legendary type for this attachment
attachmentList.compatibleweapons: All Assault Rifles and SMG's, the M600 Spitfire and the Devotion LMG

attachmentList.name: Sniper Stock
attachmentList.description: Improves weapon switch speed and aim sway.
attachmentList.commoneffect: Improves weapon switch speed and aim sway.
attachmentList.rareeffect: Quicker handling and moderate aim drift reduction. (Raising/lowering weapon is 25% faster)
attachmentList.legendaryeffect: No legendary type for this attachment
attachmentList.epiceffect: Fast handling and large aim drift reduction. (Raising/lowering weapon is 35% faster)
attachmentList.compatibleweapons: Longbow DMR, Charge Rifle, G7 Scout, Triple Take

attachmentList.name: Barrel Stabilizier
attachmentList.description: Decreases recoil.
attachmentList.commoneffect: 10% Recoil reduction and Randomness decreased by 15%.
attachmentList.rareeffect: 15% Recoil reduction and Randomness decreased by 20%
attachmentList.epiceffect: 20% Recoil reduction and Randomness decreased by 30%
attachmentList.legendaryeffect: 20% Recoil reduction and Randomness decreased by 30%, also reduces visual muzzle flash.
attachmentList.compatibleweapons: Alternator SMG, Devotion LMG, G7 Scout, Hemlok Burst AR, Longbow DMR, M600 Spitfire, R-301 Carbine, R-99, RE-45 Auto
